title: Hummel - Concerto for Trumpet.pdf
description:
This is a piano score and trumpet part for Joahnn Nepomuk Hummel&#039;s famous Concerto for E-flat for Trumpet and Orchestra. The trumpet part is notated for trumpet in E-flat. 

The music is in PDF (Acrobat) format, 300 DPI, ready to print at 8.5 x 11.

If you enjoy this download, please seed for a least a few days, as I have limited bandwidth and intend to upload a great deal more. Also, please leave comments or requests, as I have a huge library.
